com.nuvoex.fileuploader.utils

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nuvoex.fileuploader.utils.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends Object
    Utility class for logging messages to the system log. By default no message is logged. UploadQueue.setLogLevel(int) sets the log level.
